{"tid":879760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷胎8月賣淫賺生產費　嫖客熄火！反捐錢助貧母","createTime":"2018-10-28T08:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T10:57:21.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07d250e44ba8283d696f9b4f909747e5900cf8d0","tid":879760,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"泰國宋卡府一名預產期在下個月的32歲孕婦，為了籌措生產的費用，而在網路發布賣淫的訊息，訊息引發網路瘋傳，也讓孕婦立即被警方盯上約談到案，孕婦坦言自己確實要賣淫，因為她和丈夫實在沒錢能夠支付生產費用。<br />\n據《泰國世界日報》報導，孕婦表示和丈夫有一名9歲的女兒由父母照顧，自己目前懷孕8個月，預產期在11月，但在公立醫院生產就要1萬5000泰銖（約1萬5040元台幣），然而自己只是一名普通的職員，丈夫月薪也只有9000泰銖（約9024元台幣），扣除房租、水電和給父母的錢後，經常都透支，更不用說要存錢。<br />\n孕婦無奈，便瞞著丈夫發布賣淫的訊息，除了標明服務價碼，也坦言自己已經懷孕8個多月，每天最多只能接客3人，另外也販售自己的裸照和影片，更配上「泰國人不會拋棄彼此」的文字希望大家伸援。她說後來有二、三人聯繫她，發現她真的是一名孕婦，結果都放棄了買春的念頭，反而捐錢給她。<br />\n孕婦表示，由於自己是背著丈夫賣淫，也不希望丈夫知道，擔心遭到拋棄，因此拒絕任何單位的公開救助。警方事後依法辦理，但也捐錢希望給予聲助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181028/1455890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455890&d=0O7GRPL2CJy53yrnKZOtz7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1fe16517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455890&h=1c4bc136\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181028/1455890</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181028/640_a637e1af6f041f4960bf7ba4584558d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181028%2F640_a637e1af6f041f4960bf7ba4584558d6.jpg&h=c647d188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該有做到，我信"},{"pid":"e107f03a8391c9809a1ab80d5a0e1e643e411b3c","tid":879760,"uid":198583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦人哋有得揀咩？"},{"pid":"f8af71f02aa7bf6f5078faca8ec99ac4a9912b03","tid":879760,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"唉, 窮人生仔, 何必呢"},{"pid":"46fe11ff39ca70bc289cca3ee6fa230182735950","tid":879760,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8af71f02aa7bf6f5078faca8ec99ac4a9912b03","tid":879760,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"唉, 窮人生仔, 何必呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"舊後地方，老婆其實是老公資產，一定下下中出，生了天養"},{"pid":"eda29bfe32873d39bc00cb87f855033d58421e85","tid":879760,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"有咩特別，港女都係咁賺iphone啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081348bd5cc233443c08fc815f5286acc55041c3","tid":879760,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e691134f1e24747e5c6f44629706bd269b398b2","tid":879760,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"正義雞虫"},{"pid":"8acce4f4bc99233c2d0b8603dc221a5f47bc8419","tid":879760,"uid":3078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"仗義每多掏鳩輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b8a6fd7f7347ef7c97642a216431d49e5f1cc7","tid":879760,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"屌完於心有愧"},{"pid":"2caad52ba1beaae19f6108b557f777a17d97187e","tid":879760,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"有個女仲唔夠 明知窮到仆街都係咁生 其實啲大學應該捉呢啲死窮撚去解剖研究下佢地個腦"},{"pid":"1bffceb5665dfc04d30785c